Given that Captain America can punch 100 times per minute and he punches for 10 minutes, the total number of punches thrown is:

```
\boxed{
\text{{Total Punches}} = \text{{100 punches/minute}} \times \text{{10 minutes}}
}
```

Following this calculation, Captain America throws a total of 1000 punches in 10 minutes. Keep in mind that this number does not take into account any possible breaks during the given time frame.

